title: [FINERACT-593] Fix migration file V145 relate to DATE field by change default value
body:
Issue is occuring in mysql 5.7, causing migrate process error

As per latest MYSQL 5.7 [documentation](https://dev.mysql.com/doc/refman/5.7/en/sql-mode.html#sql-mode-strict)
If strict mode is enabled, '0000-00-00' is not permitted and produce an error

title: Undoing a transaction on savings account didn't set resource id correctly
body: When performing an undo transaction on a savings account, the resource id was set to the savings account itself, and not the transaction that was being reversed. This meant that in processes that depended on this value being set correctly, such as webhooks, it was impossible to determine the affected transaction.
